snippet.title: Live for Speed - South City Work in Progress
snippet.description:
Much work has gone into updating South City in Live for Speed. This video takes you on a quick tour of some of the updated and new areas.

More information and a technical background can be found at https://www.lfs.net/report-may2021-so

These scenes are taken from a Work in Progress version of South City. Some holes can be visible to the keen eye - these will be closed in the final version.

Live for Speed
https://www.lfs.net
